\lim_{n \to \infty} \left(\frac {1}{\sqrt{n^2+1}}+ \frac{1}{\sqrt{n^2+2}}+\dots +\frac{1}{\sqrt{n^2+2n}}\right)
\underbrace{\dfrac{2n}{n+1} < \dfrac{2n}{\sqrt{n^2+2n}}}_{n^2 +2n < (n+1)^2} \leq \sum_{k=1}^{2n} \dfrac1{\sqrt{n^2+k}} \leq \underbrace{\dfrac{2n}{\sqrt{n^2+1}} < \dfrac{2n}{\sqrt{n^2}}}_{n^2 < n^2+1} = 2
\frac{2n}{\sqrt{n^2+2n}}=\frac{2}{\sqrt{1+\frac{2}{n}}}\xrightarrow [n\to\infty]{}2
